{"tid":1430094,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"各位前線警員... 我想向你地講句對唔住","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T18:30:53.000Z","uid":177082,"like":20,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c723f6d30cc92f9f04c292b83bbfd14f748dc4be","tid":1430094,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:00:59.000Z","msg":"各位前線警員：<br />\n<br />\n你地日曬雨淋唔夠休息咁企出黎，真係辛苦曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n示威者情緒激動襲擊你地，令你地受驚，對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道你地都只係聽命於上頭，係上頭落Order你地先要咁對我地。<br />\n但係上頭只係一直係冷氣房都唔知現場環境，有咩就你地承受，<br />\n我地爭取唔到成立獨立調查委員會，無得徹查犯錯落錯Order嘅高層，無得還前線警員公道，對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我地五大訴求係針對政府，政府唔回應，<br />\n只推前線警員黎頂，要你地受罪，你地真係好無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實黑警只係講緊有做錯嘅警察，如果你無做錯嘅話你唔係黑警，如果你仲有良知，希望可以㩒住你嘅伙記，打細力啲，唔好打要害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位前線要繼續加油，<br />\n等到香港有民主嘅一日，你同我都唔洗再受罪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f4b02b9d80508ef9abe45fe712c9b01fee6751","tid":1430094,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ac03548dc9bd20a5223dbae58cb9b867a5b5b2","tid":1430094,"uid":285774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:05:36.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"37300a6a91ea4ffd33120ecee8731f365cc01067","tid":1430094,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"好多狗都有ac架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw阻阻大家，睇下我篇文啦<br />\n（下一步策略）警察變棄子，四招抗中共<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429837\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429837</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}